<item>
            <title>[LU-20055] NFSv4: NFS client read stale data from a file after another NFS client has updated the same file</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-20055</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1. NFS Client1 and NFS Client2 mount different NFS servers which are based the same Lustre filesystem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Topology:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
Lustre Server  -&amp;gt;  Lustre Client1(NFS Server1) -&amp;gt; NFS Client1
 &#160;            -&amp;gt;  Lustre Client2(NFS Server2) -&amp;gt; NFS Client2&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2. NFS Client1 create a file by echo &quot;aaa&quot;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
# echo aaa &amp;gt; file
# cat file
aaa&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3. NFS Client2 read data from the same file:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
# cat file
aaa &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4. NFS Client1 update data into the same file:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
# echo bbb &amp;gt; file
# cat file
bbb&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5. NFS Client2 read stale data from the same file again:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
# cat file
aaa&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
